{"tid":1750071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"票就投完喇,咁下一步應該點做?","createTime":"2019-11-24T08:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T09:40:18.000Z","uid":319943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6be769e218cb3fd4df2e79b083b5b3349425b2a1","tid":1750071,"uid":319943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T08:50:51.000Z","msg":"如題,知道今日大家都晨早流流到票站投票、而對於投完票嘅大家黎講,之後下一步要點做同有咩行動係咪值得畀大家討論下呢?<br />\n   <br />\n尤其而家理大仲有少量嘅義士係入面,咁我地係咪都要提供番啲support畀佢哋?<br />\n <br />\n所以我想籍住呢個平台同大家講雖然區議會選舉大家都好勇躍投票,都想踢走保皇黨,但與此同時都想大家諗下選舉之後仲可以有咩行動<br />\n<br />\n希望大家留個言,集思廣益"},{"pid":"d789c535515e01319bf904d894c8bcd0375c0faa","tid":1750071,"uid":78947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T08:51:20.000Z","msg":"Set deadline 然後升級"},{"pid":"759f499a700a70c649aee7a16ec19781cd33ce6b","tid":1750071,"uid":8049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T08:54:58.000Z","msg":"救poly手足 消滅黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d7e8bc166e5441a307bff7c6c841e0143c5e1cf","tid":1750071,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T08:57:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">邊區建制贏就去光復果區</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bef90cc3599cfa8c9926097981a8ff036ae13053","tid":1750071,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T08:59:05.000Z","msg":"投完票緊係去拎福袋"},{"pid":"0de43172b737aee66bfb5e8c23b08c5020979616","tid":1750071,"uid":225347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T08:59:45.000Z","msg":"睇結果先啦"},{"pid":"6e522be52918eb2c7d1f4f0df6ade7a8e68bc895","tid":1750071,"uid":282490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T09:02:17